paragraph.text:
the term Indian tribe has the meaning given the term in 
            section 4 of the Indian Self-Determination and Education
			 Assistance Act (
            25 U.S.C. 450b
          );

the term opioid means any drug having an addiction-forming or addiction-sustaining liability similar to morphine
			 or being capable of conversion into a drug having such addiction-forming
			 or addiction-sustaining liability;

subparagraph.text:
the development of detailed digital and print educational materials to accompany the online and
			 social media materials and
			 toolkit described in subparagraph (A);

specifically explain
			 how the measurements described in subparagraph (A) will provide valid
			 measures of the impact of the program described in subparagraph (A);

paragraph.text:
